title: Represents a trade correction message. See Trade Correction Message Format

Symbol.title: The symbol ID to match with the watch request.

CorrectionType.title: Either {@link net.jacobpeterson.iqfeed4j.model.feed.streaming.level1.enums.tradecorrection.CorrectionType#INSERTION} indicating a trade insert or {@link net.jacobpeterson.iqfeed4j.model.feed.streaming.level1.enums.tradecorrection.CorrectionType#DELETION} indicating a trade delete.

TradeDate.title: Date of the trade that is being inserted or deleted.

TradeTime.title: Time (including microseconds) of the trade that is being inserted or deleted.

TradePrice.title: Price of the trade that is being inserted or deleted.

TradeSize.title: Size of the trade that is being inserted or deleted.

TickID.title: Identifier for the trade that is being inserted or deleted.

TradeConditions.title: Conditions that identify the type of trade that occurred for the trade that is being inserted or deleted.

TradeMarketCenter.title: Market Center of the trade that is being inserted or deleted.
